He was the head of the [[Guldar]] trading family.

He was strongly believed to be the father of [[Torm (adventurer)|Torm]], one of the [[Knights of Myth Drannor]], bore to him by a local [[prostitute]], [[Netha]].

He had another illegitimate son, [[Oswald Guldar]]. They had no loyalty to each other.{{Cite dungeon/19/House of Cards|43}}
